paragraph: Keith Frank is an American zydeco musician from Louisiana, United States. Frank started his band, The Soileau Zydeco Band, in 1990 and is active as of 2016. He is the son of accordion player Preston Frank. Frank records on Soulwood Records.
Only the Strong Survive (1996) (Maison de Soul)
Going to See Keith Frank (2005) (Soulwood Records)
Live At Slims Yi Ki Ki, Vol. II (2014) (Soulwood Records)
